query: select f_bookings.*, d_channel.channel_sk ch_channel_sk,d_channel.channel_code,d_channel.channel_name,d_channel.channel_desc,d_channel.channel_group1,d_channel.loaddate channel_loaddate,d_channel.modifieddate channel_modifieddate,d_channel.channel_group2 from f_bookings join d_channel on f_bookings.channel_sk = d_channel.channel_sk limit 10

select f_bookings.*, d_carrier.carrier_code,d_carrier.carrier_name,d_carrier.carrier_desc,d_carrier.carrier_type,d_carrier.loaddate c_loaddate,d_carrier.modifieddate c_modifieddate from f_bookings join d_carrier  on f_bookings.carrier_sk = d_carrier.carrier_sk limit 10
